title: King

properties.value: King may refer to any of the following characters:

content:
The RuneScape Wiki also has an article on: rsw:King

King may refer to any of the following characters:

Living characters
  • King Arthur, the leader of the knights of the round table, who can be found in Camelot Castle.
  • King Awowogei, the monkey king of Ape Atoll.
  • King Baxtorian, a former elven king of the Fourth Age, now leader of Clan Cadarn.
  • King Bolren, the king of the Tree Gnome Village gnomes.
  • The Fisher King, the king of the Fisher Realm, who is involved in the Holy Grail quest.
  • King Gjuki Sorvott IV, the current ruler of the Fremennik island settlement of Jatizso.
  • King Narnode Shareen, the king of gnomes, found on the ground floor of the Grand Tree.
  • King Roald III, the current ruler of Misthalin, who lives in Varrock Palace.
  • King Thoros, the current king of Ardougne, and successor to King Lathas.
  • King Vallance, the official ruler of Asgarnia, and the father of Crown Prince Anlaf.
  • King Vargas, the king of the island of Miscellania.
Deceased characters
  • King Alvis, a former king of Keldagrim who passed away roughly 500 years ago.
  • King Argenthorg, the son of King Healthorg, and was eventually succeeded by King Narnode Shareen.
  • King Ascertes, the human husband and consort of Queen Efaritay, Queen of Hallowvale, an ancient civilisation located in what is now the swamplands of Morytania.
  • King Botolph, a former king of Varrock who is known to have held the throne during the years 17 through 19 of the Fifth Age.
  • King Claudius, who was once a ruler of Varrock some time in the Fourth Age.
  • King Gjuki Sorvott III, the fourth king of Jatizso, and the father of the island's current ruler.
  • King Healthorg, the king that lead the gnomes through their golden age during the Fourth Age.
  • King Kharedst IV, the last king of Great Kourend, before the abolishment of the monarchy.
  • King Lathas, the king of East Ardougne, killed during the Song of the Elves quest.
  • King Narras, a former mad king of Kandarin, father of King Ulthas.
  • King Raddallin, a former king of Asgarnia, the founder of modern Falador, ancestor of King Vallance and Prince Anlaf.
  • King Roald I, a former king of Misthalin, and the grandfather of King Roald III, Misthalin's current king.
  • King Roald II, a former king of Misthalin who ruled around the years 120-150 of the Fifth Age, and the father of King Roald III.
  • King Tyras, the king of West Ardougne, killed during the Regicide quest.
  • King Ulthas, former king of Kandarin, father of King Lathas and King Tyras.
Monsters
  • Dagannoth Kings, a trio of boss monsters.
  • Ice Troll King, the boss of the quest The Fremennik Isles.
  • King Black Dragon, one of the original boss monsters.
  • King kurask, the superior version of a kurask.
 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.
If an internal link led you to this disambiguation page, you may wish to change the link to point directly to the intended article.
